        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Spill the Beans]]></title>
            <link>https://english-expressions.pages.dev/blog/spill-the-beans</link>
            <guid>https://english-expressions.pages.dev/blog/spill-the-beans</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 30 Jun 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[의미]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="의미">의미<a href="https://english-expressions.pages.dev/blog/spill-the-beans#%EC%9D%98%EB%AF%B8" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 의미" title="Direct link to 의미">​</a></h3>
<p><code>Spill the beans</code>는 비밀을 누설하다, 비밀을 말하다를 뜻하는 표현입니다.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="설명">설명<a href="https://english-expressions.pages.dev/blog/spill-the-beans#%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 설명" title="Direct link to 설명">​</a></h3>
<p>이 표현은 누군가가 의도치 않게 또는 고의로 감춰야 할 정보를 말해버리는 상황에서 사용됩니다. 원래는 누군가의 비밀을 실수로 누설했을 때 자주 쓰이지만, 일부러 폭로할 때도 사용할 수 있습니다. 약간 장난스럽거나 비공식적인 분위기에서 자주 등장합니다.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="예문">예문<a href="https://english-expressions.pages.dev/blog/spill-the-beans#%EC%98%88%EB%AC%B8" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 예문" title="Direct link to 예문">​</a></h3>
<div class="text-right -mb-10 mr-2"><button class="cursor-pointer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-volume"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M15 8a5 5 0 0 1 0 8"></path><path d="M17.7 5a9 9 0 0 1 0 14"></path><path d="M6 15h-2a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h2l3.5 -4.5a.8 .8 0 0 1 1.5 .5v14a.8 .8 0 0 1 -1.5 .5l-3.5 -4.5"></path></svg></button></div><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip admonition_rEt0 alert alert--success"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>Example 1</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>She accidentally spilled the beans about the surprise party.</strong><br>
(그녀는 깜짝 파티에 대해 실수로 비밀을 누설했다.)</p></div></div>
<div class="text-right -mb-10 mr-2"><button class="cursor-pointer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-volume"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M15 8a5 5 0 0 1 0 8"></path><path d="M17.7 5a9 9 0 0 1 0 14"></path><path d="M6 15h-2a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h2l3.5 -4.5a.8 .8 0 0 1 1.5 .5v14a.8 .8 0 0 1 -1.5 .5l-3.5 -4.5"></path></svg></button></div><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip admonition_rEt0 alert alert--success"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>Example 2</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>Come on, spill the beans! What happened at the meeting?</strong><br>
(자, 말해 봐! 회의에서 무슨 일이 있었던 거야?)</p></div></div>
<div class="text-right -mb-10 mr-2"><button class="cursor-pointer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-volume"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M15 8a5 5 0 0 1 0 8"></path><path d="M17.7 5a9 9 0 0 1 0 14"></path><path d="M6 15h-2a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h2l3.5 -4.5a.8 .8 0 0 1 1.5 .5v14a.8 .8 0 0 1 -1.5 .5l-3.5 -4.5"></path></svg></button></div><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip admonition_rEt0 alert alert--success"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>Example 3</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>I wasn’t going to tell anyone, but John spilled the beans.</strong><br>
(나는 아무한테도 말할 생각이 없었는데, 존이 비밀을 말해버렸어.)</p></div></div>
